{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/561/comments/140613197.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo:22d088bf11d4..9e4dacde6cab?path=src%2Frendering%2FMarkerManager.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/561/_/diff#comment-140613197"}}, "parent": {"id": 140606727, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/561/comments/140606727.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/561/_/diff#comment-140606727"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 561, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/561.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/561"}}, "title": "Fix duplicate marker services and crash due to unset marker field"}, "content": {"raw": "Looking at [marker msg definition](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-msgs/src/44c16a60122730d932250f1f9480bfab970d7bfe/proto/ignition/msgs/marker.proto#lines-56), the enums are `GUI = 0`  and `ALL = 1`. So if someone sets to the field to `GUI` then this becomes `SetVisible(0)` and the visual will just be invisible. So I think we\u2019re using the field incorrectly here", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Looking at <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-msgs/src/44c16a60122730d932250f1f9480bfab970d7bfe/proto/ignition/msgs/marker.proto#lines-56\" rel=\"nofollow\">marker msg definition</a>, the enums are <code>GUI = 0</code>  and <code>ALL = 1</code>. So if someone sets to the field to <code>GUI</code> then this becomes <code>SetVisible(0)</code> and the visual will just be invisible. So I think we\u2019re using the field incorrectly here</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2020-03-18T03:49:36.415834+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Ian Chen", "uuid": "{eaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-